      <title>會變色的 uno 男士潤色護唇膏 給你好氣色</title>
      <link href="/posts/f9bb66ae/"/>
      <url>/posts/f9bb66ae/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/images/uploads/uno-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%BD%A4%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F-blog.jpg"></p><p>uno 男士潤色護唇膏塗抹於唇部後，顏色會由灰色變成自然健康的色澤</p><ul><li>含有保濕成分：滋潤唇部也能使垂直皺紋不那麼明顯</li><li>清爽不黏膩的妝效，顏色只會在皮膚或唇部上產生</li><li>不含薄荷醇</li><li>無香料</li></ul><p>如何使用：</p><p>擠出約 1 ~ 1.5mm，直接塗抹於唇部。</p><p>塗抹次數越多，膚色會越深。 （最終顯色效果可能因人而異。）</p><p>這是一款有色唇膏，使用後會在嘴唇上留下顏色。</p><div class="video-wrapper video-9-16"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JlxRcD_PIOM" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p><img src="/images/uploads/uno-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%88%E7%94%A8-%E6%BD%A4%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F-%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2.jpg" alt="no 男士潤色護唇膏 會變色"></p><p><img src="/images/uploads/uno-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%88%E7%94%A8-%E6%BD%A4%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F-%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B22.jpg" alt="no 男士潤色護唇 產品特色"></p><p>🛒 日本平輸特價 <strong>$260</strong></p><a class="btn-beautify red larger" href="https://shopee.tw/UNO-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%BD%A4%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A3%BD-%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8-%E7%94%B7%E6%80%A7-%E7%94%B7%E7%94%A8-%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%A6%9D%E6%84%9F-%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E6%B0%A3%E8%89%B2-i.32121963.45103582146" title="蝦皮買更便宜"><i class="fa-solid fa-shrimp"></i><span>蝦皮買更便宜</span></a><br><br>]]></content>
      
      
