      <title>平價美國 Viking Revolution 男用固體古龍水/香膏/固體香水</title>
      <link href="/posts/29783/"/>
      <url>/posts/29783/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/images/uploads/viking-revolution-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%A4%E9%BE%8D%E6%B0%B4-blog.jpg" alt="Viking Revolution 男用固體古龍水"></p><p>Viking Revolution 是來自美國一個專注於男士美容護理的品牌</p><p>他們推出的固體古龍水(香膏)使用小巧金屬盒包裝，每個 0.5OZ (約 14.18g) 方便攜帶的固體香水，隨時隨地都能使用。採用天然成分：蜂蠟、椰子油、葵花籽油。香氣選用適合男性的香調，多達 12 種香氣：</p><ol><li>檀香 sandalwood (木質)</li><li>香根草 vetiver (煙熏\木質)</li><li>雪松與松木 cedar &amp; pine (木質)</li><li>快樂鼠尾草 clary sage (草本)</li><li>香料香草 spiced vanilla (東方)</li><li>壯麗烏木 majestic oud (木質)</li><li>佛手柑 bergamot (柑橘)</li><li>甜煙草 sweet tobacco (東方\木質)</li><li>秘魯聖木 palo santo (木質)</li><li>威士忌咖啡 coffee &amp; whiskey (咖啡酒香)</li><li>海鹽 sea salt (海洋)</li><li>波本威士忌與麂皮 bourbon &amp; suede (酒香&#x2F;皮革)</li></ol><div class="video-wrapper video-9-16"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aTUgFLUZbto" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p><img src="/images/uploads/viking-revolution-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%A4%E9%BE%8D%E6%B0%B4-%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B21.jpg" alt="Viking Revolution 男用固體古龍水 - 隨身帶著走"></p><p><img src="/images/uploads/viking-revolution-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%A4%E9%BE%8D%E6%B0%B4-%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B22.jpg" alt="Viking Revolution 男用固體古龍水 - 天然成分"></p><p><img src="/images/uploads/viking-revolution-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%A4%E9%BE%8D%E6%B0%B4-%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B23.jpg" alt="Viking Revolution 男用固體古龍水 - 使用方式"></p><p>🛒 美國平輸特價 <strong>$149</strong></p><a class="btn-beautify red larger" href="https://shopee.tw/Viking-Revolution-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%A4%E9%BE%8D%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%99%E8%86%8F-%E5%9B%BA%E9%AB%94%E9%A6%99%E6%B0%B4-%E6%9C%A8%E8%B3%AA%E8%AA%BF-%E7%9A%AE%E9%9D%A9%E8%AA%BF-%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8-i.32121963.45653178754" title="蝦皮買更便宜"><i class="fa-solid fa-shrimp"></i><span>蝦皮買更便宜</span></a><br><br>]]></content>
      
      
