      <title>帶來水潤光澤肌膚的粉餅 KissMe Ferme 金燦保濕粉餅</title>
      <link href="/posts/43190/"/>
      <url>/posts/43190/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/images/uploads/kissme-ferme-%E7%B2%89%E9%A4%85-blog.jpg" alt="KissMe Ferme 金燦保濕粉餅盒以及替換用粉餅蕊"></p><p>帶來水潤光澤肌膚的粉餅，防曬係數 SPF25 PA++ 能夠遮蓋細紋、毛孔和暗沉，一年四季均可使用，不脫落服貼配方，讓你在晚上之前都不必擔心皺紋！</p><ul><li>貼合不脫妝，撫平表情紋。</li><li>長時間遮蓋細紋、毛孔與暗沉。</li><li>滑順貼膚，鎖住肌膚水分。</li><li>蘊含多種保濕精華，滋潤滿滿。</li><li>緊密貼合，持久不脫妝。</li></ul><p>添加多種保濕成分：<br>玻尿酸、膠原蛋白、蜂王漿萃取、洋甘菊萃取、摩洛哥堅果油（皆為保濕成分）</p><p><img src="/images/uploads/%E9%A1%8F%E8%89%B2%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83.jpg" alt="KissMe Ferme 金燦保濕粉餅顏色參考"></p><div class="video-wrapper video-9-16"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kwwtokHh5bY" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p>🛒 日本平輸特價 $460（粉餅盒）&#x2F; $360 （粉餅蕊）</p><a class="btn-beautify red larger" href="https://shopee.tw/KissMe-FERME-%E9%87%91%E7%87%A6%E4%BF%9D%E6%BF%95%E7%B2%89%E9%A4%85%E7%9B%92-%E6%9B%BF%E6%8F%9B%E7%94%A8%E7%B2%89%E9%A4%85%E8%95%8A-%E5%9B%9B%E8%89%B2%E5%8F%AF%E9%81%B8-%E9%81%AE%E7%91%95-%E5%AE%9A%E5%A6%9D-%E9%98%B2%E6%9B%AC-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A3%BD-%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8-i.32121963.27622726683" title="蝦皮買更便宜"><i class="fa-solid fa-shrimp"></i><span>蝦皮買更便宜</span></a><br><br>]]></content>
      
      
